      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's easy on the wallet? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for many more miles! It shows some honest character and wear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid and dependable choice for anyone seeking great value. Come see why this practical ride is perfect for your next journey!",
