    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious project or a source for spare parts. The engine needs a complete overhaul to be functional, and the transmission is currently slipping and unreliable. Additionally, the body shows signs of significant wear and minor rust, while the interior requires deep cleaning and repair. It is not currently road-worthy, but it offers a solid foundation for a dedicated mechanic or hobbyist.",
