    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I'm parting with this beauty and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved. Whether you're commuting or hitting the road for a weekend trip, this car is ready to go. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
