      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example excels in mechanical engagement, with the Double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous throttle response. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates, and the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal traction through the corners. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection to maintain peak internal tolerances. While the aesthetic shows minor patina from spirited use, the hydraulic steering remains communicative and the suspension geometry is dialed for the enthusiast who prioritizes analog performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. Inspect in person.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care. The exterior finish maintains a brilliant luster, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a pristine environment; the upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard remains crack-free, and every electronic component\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operates as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history that proves its mechanical integrity. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring it's ready for the road immediately. It drives with the tight, responsive feel of a car that has been genuinely respected by its owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
